	(text "Maybe something like this:?\n------------------ MIPI CSI INPUT ------------------\n\nCM4_CLK+  → MUX1_INA+\nCM4_CLK–  → MUX1_INA–\n\nCM4_D0+   → MUX2_INB+\nCM4_D0–   → MUX2_INB–\n\nCM4_D1+   → MUX3_INC+\nCM4_D1–   → MUX3_INC–\n\n------------------ MUX LAYER 1 ---------------------\n\nMUX1_OUTA ± → CAM1_CLK±\nMUX1_OUTB ± → CAM2_CLK±\n\nMUX2_OUTA ± → CAM1_D0±\nMUX2_OUTB ± → CAM2_D0±\n\nMUX3_OUTA ± → CAM1_D1±\nMUX3_OUTB ± → CAM2_D1±\n\nSEL1 (GPIO) → MUX1_SEL, MUX2_SEL, MUX3_SEL\n\n------------------ MUX LAYER 2 ---------------------\n\nMUX4 takes CAM1/CAM2 output and muxes with CAM3/CAM4 similarly.\n\nSEL2 (GPIO) → MUX4_SEL, MUX5_SEL, MUX6_SEL\n\n------------------ CAMERA OUTPUTS ------------------\n\nCAM1 → FPC Connector 1\nCAM2 → FPC Connector 2\nCAM3 → FPC Connector 3\nCAM4 → FPC Connector 4\n\n------------------ POWER ---------------------------\n\n3.3V → All MUX VDD pins\n100 nF → GND (close)\n10 µF → GND (bulk)\n\n------------------ OPTIONAL I2C MUX ----------------\n\nCM4_SDA → PCA9545A_SDA\nCM4_SCL → PCA9545A_SCL\n\nPCA9545A_CH1 → CAM1 SDA/SCL\nPCA9545A_CH2 → CAM2 SDA/SCL\nPCA9545A_CH3 → CAM3 SDA/SCL\nPCA9545A_CH4 → CAM4 SDA/SCL\n\n----------------------------------------------------\n"
		(exclude_from_sim no)
		(at 206.756 155.702 0)
		(effects
			(font
				(size 0.889 0.889)
			)
		)
		(uuid "4023f360-5295-412e-a0eb-7096581d38bb")
	)
