	)
	(text "maybe something like this:?\n------------------ DIGITAL AUDIO ------------------\n\nCM4_GPIO18  (I2S BCLK) -----------------> WM8960_BCLK\nCM4_GPIO19  (I2S LRCLK) ----------------> WM8960_LRCLK\nCM4_GPIO21  (I2S DOUT)  ----------------> WM8960_ADCDAT\nCM4_GPIO20  (I2S DIN)   <---------------- WM8960_DACDAT\n\nCM4_SDA1 -------------------------------> WM8960_SDA\nCM4_SCL1 -------------------------------> WM8960_SCL\n\nPullups: SDA → 4.7k → 3.3V  \n          SCL → 4.7k → 3.3V\n\n------------------ POWER --------------------------\n\n3.3V → AVDD (10 µF + 0.1 µF to GND)\n3.3V → DVDD (10 µF + 0.1 µF to GND)\n3.3V → HPVDD (10 µF + 0.1 µF to GND)\n5.0V → SPKVDD (10 µF + 0.1 µF to GND)\n\nWM8960_GND → GND\n\n---------------- HEADPHONE JACK -------------------\n\nWM8960_HPLOUT → 100Ω → JACK_TIP (Left)\nWM8960_HPROUT → 100Ω → JACK_RING (Right)\nGND --------------------→ JACK_SLEEVE (Ground)\n\nOptional:\nJACK_TIP  → 100 pF → GND\nJACK_RING → 100 pF → GND\n\n---------------- SPEAKER OUTPUT -------------------\n\nWM8960_SPK_P → 10 µH → Speaker+\nWM8960_SPK_N → 10 µH → Speaker–\n\nOptional LC:\nAfter each inductor → 470nF → GND\n\n---------------------------------------------------\n"
		(exclude_from_sim no)
		(at 217.424 309.118 0)
		(effects
